Miss Ye went to meet him.

00:01:34.760 --> 00:01:35.600
Mr. Xu.

00:01:37.420 --> 00:01:38.820
(Xu Dashan)

00:01:44.680 --> 00:01:45.520
Miss Ye,

00:01:46.440 --> 00:01:48.440
you teamed up with Gu Yixiao
to set a trap.

00:01:49.640 --> 00:01:51.560
Living life on the edge like this

00:01:51.560 --> 00:01:52.720
is not easy, right?

00:01:54.800 --> 00:01:56.320
You'd be better be with me.

00:01:58.840 --> 00:02:00.160
Mr. Xu, you're just teasing me.

00:02:00.560 --> 00:02:02.440
If you have any other requests,
just say it.

00:02:02.900 --> 00:02:04.080
We'll do our best to meet you.

00:02:07.240 --> 00:02:08.640
You know what I mean.

00:02:10.420 --> 00:02:11.940
To win someone over, win their heart.

00:02:12.400 --> 00:02:13.680
If you want to achieve your goal,

00:02:14.160 --> 00:02:15.360
you need some strategy:

00:02:16.080 --> 00:02:17.040
show weakness,

00:02:17.720 --> 00:02:18.640
appear pitiful,

00:02:19.960 --> 00:02:22.560
and spark a man's instinct
to protect and claim you,

00:02:23.240 --> 00:02:24.600
making him lose control over you

00:02:25.400 --> 00:02:26.640
and unable to keep hold of you.

00:02:27.600 --> 00:02:30.120
Once his emotions are slowly
in your hands,

00:02:31.120 --> 00:02:32.080
that's when you've won.

00:02:36.800 --> 00:02:38.520
Lately, someone told me

00:02:38.720 --> 00:02:40.440
I'm facing a bloodshed misfortune.

00:02:40.720 --> 00:02:43.720
I need to connect with someone deeply

00:02:45.040 --> 00:02:46.960
with someone born
in a Yin hour and Yin month.

00:02:50.760 --> 00:02:51.600
Mr. Xu,

00:02:52.200 --> 00:02:53.360
you're flattering me.

00:02:54.080 --> 00:02:55.400
But your request,

00:02:56.320 --> 00:02:57.560
I might not be able to meet it.

00:03:03.200 --> 00:03:04.080
I know. (Support Admin Watch on
kissasia.cam or kisskh.org)

